                                    "hidden": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "speaker": "vicky",
                            "dialogue": "Whoa! Look at this massive door! It looks like it's made of titanium. And again, it opens with a code...",
                            "nextFrame": "inception4_01"
                        },
                        "inception4_01": {
                            "id": "inception4_01",
                            "dialogue": "You’ve already completed two tasks, miss! You can do it!",
                            "speaker": "robot",
                            "nextFrame": "inception3_06"
                        },
                        "inception4_02": {
                            "id": "inception4_02",
                            "dialogue": "I have no doubt! Wait! Do you hear that?!",
                            "speaker": "vicky",
                            "nextFrame": "inception3_03"
                        },
                        "inception4_03": {
                            "id": "inception4_03",
                            "dialogue": "There's definitely someone behind the door!",
                            "speaker": "robot",
                            "nextFrame": "inception3_04"
                        },
                        "inception4_04": {
                            "id": "inception4_04",
                            "dialogue": "What if it’s Mitnik?! Do you have a weapon?",
                            "speaker": "vicky",
                            "nextFrame": "inception4_05"
                        },
                        "inception4_05": {
                            "id": "inception4_05",
                            "dialogue": "No, miss! I cannot harm a human!",
                            "speaker": "robot",
                            "nextFrame": "inception4_06"
                        },
                        "inception4_06": {
                            "id": "inception4_06",
                            "dialogue": "People are different, and some could really use a little harm. I’ll grab my knife. It’s better than nothing! Let’s try to catch Mitnik off guard!",
                            "speaker": "vicky",
                            "nextFrame": "inception4_07"
                        },
                        "inception4_07": {
                            "id": "inception4_07",
                            "dialogue": "I don’t think that’s a very good idea, miss! If I were you, I’d be more cautious! I’m scared!",
                            "speaker": "robot",
                            "nextFrame": "inception4_08"
                        },
                        "inception4_08": {
                            "id": "inception4_08",
                            "dialogue": "The scariest thing is not finishing all the tasks within six hours! Then humanity is doomed!",
                            "speaker": "vicky",
                            "nextFrame": "inception4_09"
                        },
                        "inception4_09": {
